reviewText: The only reason I gave it a 1 star, is that the cover is misleading. Some of these musicans are not on this dvd, it realy is a dvd of a live concert recorded yrs' later. It is realy the REO Speedwagon Live Plus dvd, witch is great, but I wanted one that contained Gary Richrath on lead guitar. The cover & even the dvd cover show him, but it is not him on the dvd when played it's Dave Amato. DON"T BUY IF YOU ALREADY ON (REO SPEEDWAGON LIVE PLUS)!!!!
